room_title: Escape room "Room 1301" by Escape from Mystery Manor in Boise
room_description: Room 1301 inside Mystery Manor is not your typical tourist trap, it is the place where evil dwells, or so we've been told. And those who face it in the pursuit of a thrill may never be able to tell about their experience inside. After all, sometimes those who check-in, never check out! Are you ready to check-in?
